### JC-3-2.鏁村悎MyBatis

鈥�	鏁村悎瀹孞Unit涓嬮潰鍐嶆潵璇翠竴涓嬫暣鍚圡yBatis锛岃繖涓妧鏈槸澶ч儴鍒嗗叕鍙搁兘瑕佷娇鐢ㄧ殑鎶€鏈紝鍔″繀鎺屾彙銆傚鏋滃Spring鏁村悎MyBatis涓嶇啛鎮夌殑灏忎紮浼村ソ濂藉涔犱竴涓嬶紝涓嬮潰鍒椾妇鍑哄師濮嬫暣鍚堢殑鍏ㄩ儴鍐呭锛屼互閰嶇疆绫荤殑褰㈠紡涓轰緥杩涜

- 瀵煎叆鍧愭爣锛孧yBatis鍧愭爣涓嶈兘灏戯紝Spring鏁村悎MyBatis杩樻湁鑷繁涓撶敤鐨勫潗鏍囷紝姝ゅSpring杩涜鏁版嵁搴撴搷浣滅殑jdbc鍧愭爣鏄繀椤荤殑锛屽墿涓嬭繕鏈塵ysql椹卞姩鍧愭爣锛屾湰渚嬩腑浣跨敤浜咲ruid鏁版嵁婧愶紝杩欎釜鍊掓槸鍙互涓嶈

  ```XML
  <dependencies>
      <dependency>
          <groupId>com.alibaba</groupId>
          <artifactId>druid</artifactId>
          <version>1.1.16</version>
      </dependency>
      <dependency>
          <groupId>org.mybatis</groupId>
          <artifactId>mybatis</artifactId>
          <version>3.5.6</version>
      </dependency>
      <dependency>
          <groupId>mysql</groupId>
          <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
          <version>5.1.47</version>
      </dependency>
      <!--1.瀵煎叆mybatis涓巗pring鏁村悎鐨刯ar鍖�-->
      <dependency>
          <groupId>org.mybatis</groupId>
          <artifactId>mybatis-spring</artifactId>
          <version>1.3.0</version>
      </dependency>
      <!--瀵煎叆spring鎿嶄綔鏁版嵁搴撳繀閫夌殑鍖�-->
      <dependency>
          <groupId>org.springframework</groupId>
          <artifactId>spring-jdbc</artifactId>
          <version>5.2.10.RELEASE</version>
      </dependency>
  </dependencies>
  ```

- Spring鏍稿績閰嶇疆

  ```JAVA
  @Configuration
  @ComponentScan("com.itheima")
