  public class SpringConfig {
  }
  ```

- MyBatis瑕佷氦缁橲pring鎺ョ鐨刡ean

  ```JAVA
  //瀹氫箟mybatis涓撶敤鐨勯厤缃被
  @Configuration
  public class MyBatisConfig {
  //    瀹氫箟鍒涘缓SqlSessionFactory瀵瑰簲鐨刡ean
      @Bean
      public SqlSessionFactoryBean sqlSessionFactory(DataSource dataSource){
          //SqlSessionFactoryBean鏄敱mybatis-spring鍖呮彁渚涚殑锛屼笓鐢ㄤ簬鏁村悎鐢ㄧ殑瀵硅薄
          SqlSessionFactoryBean sfb = new SqlSessionFactoryBean();
          //璁剧疆鏁版嵁婧愭浛浠ｅ師濮嬮厤缃腑鐨別nvironments鐨勯厤缃�
          sfb.setDataSource(dataSource);
          //璁剧疆绫诲瀷鍒悕鏇夸唬鍘熷閰嶇疆涓殑typeAliases鐨勯厤缃�
          sfb.setTypeAliasesPackage("com.itheima.domain");
          return sfb;
      }
  //    瀹氫箟鍔犺浇鎵€鏈夌殑鏄犲皠閰嶇疆
      @Bean
      public MapperScannerConfigurer mapperScannerConfigurer(){
          MapperScannerConfigurer msc = new MapperScannerConfigurer();
          msc.setBasePackage("com.itheima.dao");
          return msc;
      }
  
  }
  ```

- 鏁版嵁婧愬搴旂殑bean锛屾澶勪娇鐢―ruid鏁版嵁婧�

  ```JAVA
  @Configuration
  public class JdbcConfig {
      @Value("${jdbc.driver}")
      private String driver;
      @Value("${jdbc.url}")
      private String url;
      @Value("${jdbc.username}")
      private String userName;
      @Value("${jdbc.password}")
      private String password;
  
      @Bean("dataSource")
      public DataSource dataSource(){
          DruidDataSource ds = new DruidDataSource();
          ds.setDriverClassName(driver);
          ds.setUrl(url);
          ds.setUsername(userName);
          ds.setPassword(password);
          return ds;
      }
  }
  ```

- 鏁版嵁搴撹繛鎺ヤ俊鎭紙properties鏍煎紡锛�

  ```properties
  jdbc.driver=com.mysql.jdbc.Driver
  jdbc.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/spring_db?useSSL=false
  jdbc.username=root
  jdbc.password=root
  ```

  涓婅堪鏍煎紡鍩烘湰涓婃槸绠€鏍煎紡浜嗭紝瑕佸啓鐨勪笢瑗胯繕鐪熶笉灏戙€備笅闈㈢湅鐪婼pringBoot鏁村悎MyBaits鏍煎紡

