鈥�	瀹屼簡锛屽氨杩欎箞澶氾紝娌′簡銆傛湁浜哄氨寰堢撼闂凤紝杩欏氨缁撴潫浜嗭紵瀵癸紝杩欏氨缁撴潫浜嗭紝SpringBoot鎶婇厤缃腑鎵€鏈夊彲鑳藉嚭鐜扮殑閫氱敤閰嶇疆閮界畝鍖栦簡銆備笅闈㈠氨鍙互鍐欎竴涓婱yBatis绋嬪簭杩愯闇€瑕佺殑Dao锛堟垨鑰匨apper锛夊氨鍙互杩愯浜�

**瀹炰綋绫�**

```JAVA
public class Book {
    private Integer id;
    private String type;
    private String name;
    private String description;
}
```

**鏄犲皠鎺ュ彛锛圖ao锛�**

```JAVA
@Mapper
public interface BookDao {
    @Select("select * from tbl_book where id = #{id}")
    public Book getById(Integer id);
}
```

**娴嬭瘯绫�**

```JAVA
@SpringBootTest
class Springboot05MybatisApplicationTests {
    @Autowired
    private BookDao bookDao;
    @Test
    void contextLoads() {
        System.out.println(bookDao.getById(1));
    }
}
