鈥�	瀹炰綋绫荤殑寮€鍙戝彲浠ヨ嚜鍔ㄩ€氳繃宸ュ叿鎵嬪伐鐢熸垚get/set鏂规硶锛岀劧鍚庤鐩杢oString()鏂规硶锛屾柟渚胯皟璇曪紝绛夌瓑銆備笉杩囪繖涓€濂楁搷浣滀功鍐欏緢绻佺悙锛屾湁瀵瑰簲鐨勫伐鍏峰彲浠ュ府鍔╂垜浠畝鍖栧紑鍙戯紝浠嬬粛涓€涓皬宸ュ叿锛宭ombok銆�

鈥�	Lombok锛屼竴涓狫ava绫诲簱锛屾彁渚涗簡涓€缁勬敞瑙ｏ紝绠€鍖朠OJO瀹炰綋绫诲紑鍙戯紝SpringBoot鐩墠榛樿闆嗘垚浜唋ombok鎶€鏈紝骞舵彁渚涗簡瀵瑰簲鐨勭増鏈帶鍒讹紝鎵€浠ュ彧闇€瑕佹彁渚涘搴旂殑鍧愭爣鍗冲彲锛屽湪pom.xml涓坊鍔爈ombok鐨勫潗鏍囥€�

```XML
<dependencies>
    <!--lombok-->
    <dependency>
        <groupId>org.projectlombok</groupId>
        <artifactId>lombok</artifactId>
    </dependency>
</dependencies>
```

鈥�	浣跨敤lombok鍙互閫氳繃涓€涓敞瑙Data瀹屾垚涓€涓疄浣撶被瀵瑰簲鐨刧etter锛宻etter锛宼oString锛宔quals锛宧ashCode绛夋搷浣滅殑蹇€熸坊鍔�

```JAVA
import lombok.Data;
@Data
public class Book {
    private Integer id;
    private String type;
    private String name;
    private String description;
}
```

鈥�	鍒拌繖閲屽疄浣撶被灏卞仛濂戒簡锛屾槸涓嶆槸姣斾笉浣跨敤lombok绠€鍖栧ソ澶氾紝杩欑宸ュ叿鍦↗ava寮€鍙戜腑杩樻湁N澶氾紝鍚庨潰璇剧▼涓亣鍒颁簡鑳界敤鐨勪笢瑗挎椂锛屽湪涓嶅鍔犲悇浣嶅皬浼欎即澶ч噺鐨勫涔犳椂闂寸殑鎯呭喌涓嬶紝灏介噺澶氱粰澶у浠嬬粛涓€浜�

**鎬荤粨**

1. 瀹炰綋绫诲埗浣�
2. 浣跨敤lombok绠€鍖栧紑鍙�
   - 瀵煎叆lombok鏃犻渶鎸囧畾鐗堟湰锛岀敱SpringBoot鎻愪緵鐗堟湰
   - @Data娉ㄨВ



#### 2.鏁版嵁灞傚紑鍙戔€斺€斿熀纭€CRUD

鈥�	鏁版嵁灞傚紑鍙戞湰娆′娇鐢∕yBatisPlus鎶€鏈紝鏁版嵁婧愪娇鐢ㄥ墠闈㈠涔犵殑Druid锛屽閮藉浜嗛兘鐢ㄤ笂

**姝ラ鈶�**锛氬鍏yBatisPlus涓嶥ruid瀵瑰簲鐨剆tarter锛屽綋鐒秏ysql鐨勯┍鍔ㄤ笉鑳藉皯

```xml
<dependencies>
    <dependency>
        <groupId>com.baomidou</groupId>
        <artifactId>mybatis-plus-boot-starter</artifactId>
        <version>3.4.3</version>
    </dependency>
    <dependency>
        <groupId>com.alibaba</groupId>
        <artifactId>druid-spring-boot-starter</artifactId>
        <version>1.2.6</version>
    </dependency>
    <dependency>
        <groupId>mysql</groupId>
        <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
        <scope>runtime</scope>
    </dependency>
</dependencies>
```

**姝ラ鈶�**锛氶厤缃暟鎹簱杩炴帴鐩稿叧鐨勬暟鎹簮閰嶇疆

```YAML
server:
  port: 80

spring:
  datasource:
    druid:
      driver-class-name: com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver
      url: jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ssm_db?serverTimezone=UTC
      username: root
      password: root
```

**姝ラ鈶�**锛氫娇鐢∕P鐨勬爣鍑嗛€氱敤鎺ュ彛BaseMapper鍔犻€熷紑鍙戯紝鍒繕浜咢Mapper鍜屾硾鍨嬬殑鎸囧畾

```JAVA
@Mapper
public interface BookDao extends BaseMapper<Book> {
}
```

**姝ラ鈶�**锛氬埗浣滄祴璇曠被娴嬭瘯缁撴灉锛岃繖涓祴璇曠被鍒朵綔鏄釜濂戒範鎯紝涓嶈繃鍦ㄤ紒涓氬紑鍙戜腑寰€寰€閮戒负鍔犻€熷紑鍙戣烦杩囨姝ワ紝涓旇涓旂弽鎯滃惂

```JAVA
package com.itheima.dao;

import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.conditions.query.LambdaQueryWrapper;
import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.conditions.query.QueryWrapper;
import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.metadata.IPage;
import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.extension.plugins.pagination.Page;
import com.itheima.domain.Book;
import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;
import org.springframework.boot.test.context.SpringBootTest;

@SpringBootTest
public class BookDaoTestCase {

    @Autowired
    private BookDao bookDao;

    @Test
    void testGetById(){
        System.out.println(bookDao.selectById(1));
    }

    @Test
    void testSave(){
        Book book = new Book();
        book.setType("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁123");
        book.setName("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁123");
        book.setDescription("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁123");
        bookDao.insert(book);
    }

    @Test
    void testUpdate(){
        Book book = new Book();
        book.setId(17);
        book.setType("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁abcdefg");
        book.setName("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁123");
        book.setDescription("娴嬭瘯鏁版嵁123");
        bookDao.updateById(book);
    }

    @Test
    void testDelete(){
        bookDao.deleteById(16);
    }

    @Test
    void testGetAll(){
        bookDao.selectList(null);
    }
}
```

